<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger; background-color:silver; color:#000;" class="fn summary">Charles Chaplin</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="padding: 0px; padding-top: 2px; text-align:center; font-size:100%;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Charlie_Chaplin.jpg" class="image" title="Charlie Chaplin.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/00/Charlie_Chaplin.jpg" width="225" height="321" border="0" /></a><br />
